HEADWORD: Piceous
<hw>Pic"e*ous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>piceus</ets>, fr. <ets>pix</ets>, <ets>picis</ets>, pitch.]</ety>
